    {
      "parameters": {
        "promptType": "define",
        "text": "=You are writing a concise daily sprint digest for a Product/Engineering team lead.\n\nSprint data:\n- Total items: {{ $json.total }}\n- Done: {{ $json.done }}, In Progress: {{ $json.inProgress }}, To Do: {{ $json.toDo }}, In Review: {{ $json.inReview }}\n- Blocked items: {{ JSON.stringify($json.blocked) }}\n- At-risk (overdue) items: {{ JSON.stringify($json.atRisk) }}\n\nWrite a short, scannable standup digest with three sections:\n1. Progress snapshot (one line, e.g. \"3/11 items complete, on track\")\n2. Blockers needing attention (list each blocked item with its key and summary)\n3. At-risk items (list each overdue item with its key, summary, and how many days overdue)\n\nKeep it under 150 words, professional tone, use bullet points.",
        "batching": {}
      },
